metadata.name: ACK Collector Badge #1/50
metadata.description:
Collector Badges for dope ACK holders. 

With this Badge you can enter any museum in the world and draw Pepe's on famous paintings without being thrown in jail.

This Badge also protects you against divorce should your wife/spouse get tired of your tireless jpeg trading. 

This Badge protects you against FOMO and Cope. 

This Badge hereby grants you the right to saying phrases like "WAGMI" and "GM" without being made fun of by normies.

This Badge also gives you the right to laugh at the guy in the Lambo because he will most definitely not have a Badge.

For more details, plz ask devs for help

(this work was a gift from Nessgraphics when i retired from the government, which he was kind enough to let me use as my collector badge)
